        "created_at": "2020-01-07T05:17:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Yup. Just had a 2017 Foillard Corcelette. Quite ripe, nearly as ripe as the '15. I haven\u2019t had any 2017 Rhones, but do find some vintage similarity between the two regions (not surprising given their proximity/soil).</p>",
